# Deploy via Git (same as `railway-deploy.mdc`)

**Canonical rule:** **`.cursor/rules/railway-deploy.mdc`**

**Summary:** **`git add` → `git commit` → `git push`** (e.g. to **`main`**) for normal production deploys. **`railway up --no-gitignore`** only when the user explicitly wants a CLI upload or push-based deploy is unavailable.
